Owned by an older couple. Conveniently located near a parking lot, in the middle of neighbourhood. Sells a variety of drinks, both cold and not. Sells some groceries, and a variety of snacks. Prices are the same as one would expect at a typical neighbourhood Mama shop. Interior looks old, but is quite clean.
